57
00:04:21,460 --> 00:04:24,860
And we have to wonder, like, what will that look like and look for whatever that is?

58
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:25,860
Yeah.

59
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:26,860
Yeah.

60
00:04:26,860 --> 00:04:30,300
