61
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:34,400
It's similar to a lonely person asking, where is everybody?

62
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:37,380
And you tell that person, look, you are not that attractive.

63
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:40,420
You won't expect potential partners to be next to you.

64
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:42,780
You need to put some work into finding them.

65
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:47,340
You know, either go to dating sites or at the very least look through your windows.

66
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:50,580
And Fermi didn't build the telescope to search for any aliens.

67
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:55,140
Well, there's something to be said for the idea that would we even know what to look

