00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:45,960
today, but still the expected value of the future is still dominated by that thick tail

184
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:48,480
high end of the distribution scenario.

185
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:54,400
Yeah, I completely agree that we can get our inspiration from the tail of the distribution

186
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,600
because we are probably somewhere in the middle.

187
00:12:57,080 --> 00:13:03,080
And the question is, how far does the tail go and whether it's dominated by AI, for

188
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:05,760
example, rather than biological systems.

189
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:09,520
And what are the capabilities for propulsion in particular?

190
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:13,160
How far can you go over a billion years at what speed?

