00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:34,040
those probes could fill up the Milky Way galaxy, even if they are driven by chemical

195
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:38,400
propulsion. So we really don't know how far the tail goes.

196
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:43,600
And as you say, Robin, one way to find it is by looking at the sky.

